message.body: Hey. Been running around and on the phone with my folks. You still cooking? Wanna meet for a drink?
Yeah if you want some of this it will be ready in 15 20 min
Sure, that would be nice. I don't have a key so I'll text when I get there.

Thanks for the bisque, by the way!
Ok I'll probably leave here around 6 if you want to walk over together
Sounds good. I'm on 10th, so just text me when you're leaving Daniel's and I'll meet you.
Ok. Feels like it might rain all night...
I'm gona wait until 630 or 7 to serif the rain stops
Meet me at 10 n bainbridge at 630
